      "recording_attendee_id": "5811fe17-495f-468c-bb4a-6fb4f6cf99f9",
      "order_number": 8,
      "text": "Oh okay I'm sorry we we've just been busy, I'm thinking I don't have a couple of them. I think we're supposed to get a call at the beginning of this year but we've been picking up so many properties that um that's that's been my focus really is that"
    },
