      "recording_attendee_id": "30118c88-1742-4406-8aa0-9f785617bc43",
      "order_number": 11,
      "text": "real quick though. Diana basic and I know you're busy, so I basically wanted to tell you um when we were on the call you had mentioned you were paying only nine hundred and ninety-nine last year. I can honor, I can honor that this month. So that's why I wanted to see you know?"
